{"tid":1290650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察有委任證，社工一樣有註冊證","createTime":"2019-07-06T14:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T06:31:18.000Z","uid":39752,"like":123,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"90b9511b5c67d9568d2b65b679cbc487ad249869","tid":1290650,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無註冊係唔可以自稱社工<br />\n根據社會工作者註冊條例，冒認社工係違法<br />\n如果有人自稱社工，大家可以先核實佢係咪註冊社工先<br />\n特別係啲企圖自殺個案又或者接鬼走嘅情況</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n註冊咗嘅先至可以自稱社工，佢哋一定有張帶有獨立編號嘅證<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBXx1N4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBXx1N4.png&h=c2b4c605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲機構會要求帶埋機構本身嘅證明文件，例如明愛外展會有埋明愛張證<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXQDcVd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXQDcVd.png&h=a73ce4dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（以上說明圖片來自明愛公開資料：<br />\n<a href=\"http://ycs.caritas.org.hk/cyberyouth/notice.htm）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fycs.caritas.org.hk%2Fcyberyouth%2Fnotice.htm%EF%BC%89&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=7c00ac1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ycs.caritas.org.hk/cyberyouth/notice.htm）</a><br />\n<br />\n所有註冊社工名單都係公開，可以入名或入編號查到<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swrb.org.hk/tc/SearchDetail.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swrb.org.hk%2Ftc%2FSearchDetail.asp&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=ed29c264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swrb.org.hk/tc/SearchDetail.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀<br />\n社工註冊局：若發現有人冒認社工，可以報警<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/98339/%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5%E8%A8%BB%E5%86%8A%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%9A%E8%8B%A5%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%86%92%E8%AA%8D%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F98339%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25A8%25BB%25E5%2586%258A%25E5%25B1%2580%25EF%25BC%259A%25E8%258B%25A5%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2586%2592%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%2F&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=5f4d43c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/98339/%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5%E8%A8%BB%E5%86%8A%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%9A%E8%8B%A5%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%86%92%E8%AA%8D%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6/</a>"},{"pid":"2fff5521871becffddf74f5936dbfe1f3bbe99d9","tid":1290650,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30188b540481f01cc6303e8f63139e964d7e8817","tid":1290650,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2547be561caff59b77384d02ccf46cfdaeedc131","tid":1290650,"uid":268106,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4f5c08f865586618d2a977e493afc1dd119d53eb","tid":1290650,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:41:13.000Z","msg":"<code>我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我 我投訴你</code>"},{"pid":"ffdce47dd6d141fa23597a12fe2d5299438a7d9a","tid":1290650,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:44:07.000Z","msg":"俾乜鳩負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c961b583f8595a765bd0f4bdaf88e6cbf059f18","tid":1290650,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:44:11.000Z","msg":"如果係親中社工又點睇<br />\n你當刻分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"