e9%259f%25b3%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2HZ3IDDofDqYU8hOmX27aSkupzX-u1HXBRndwRaFOsi9P3E1KpmpQKEaA&h=6eb2f126\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e5%89%af%e5%88%8a/article/20190630/s00005/1561832238083/%e7%b7%a9%e8%a1%9d%e9%81%94%e4%ba%ba%e7%a4%be%e5%b7%a5%e9%99%b3%e8%99%b9%e7%a7%80-%e8%a1%9d%e7%aa%81%e7%8f%be%e5%a0%b4-%e8%ad%a6%e5%af%9f%e9%a1%98%e6%84%8f%e8%81%86%e8%81%bd%e7%9a%84%e8%81%b2%e9%9f%b3?fbclid=IwAR2HZ3IDDofDqYU8hOmX27aSkupzX-u1HXBRndwRaFOsi9P3E1KpmpQKEaA</a><br />\n<br />\n參考返"},{"pid":"b76355912ff7fe2a2a1356f771889987493551cb","tid":1290650,"uid":26050,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:47:20.000Z","msg":"另外,最撚親中嗰間一定係新家園協會<br />\n<br />\n而青協個底都紅紅地<br />\n自己睇路"},{"pid":"9ac7831a6abc53f82af6d05a75d6e76a81be57f4","tid":1290650,"uid":168818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"3df1ebd19f64bf1979436a102bfc697c83a62d8c","tid":1290650,"uid":39752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3c961b583f8595a765bd0f4bdaf88e6cbf059f18","tid":1290650,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:44:11.000Z","msg":"如果係親中社工又點睇<br />\n你當刻分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:48:51.000Z","msg":"唔理佢親唔親中佢都要有註冊<br />\n無註冊，冒認社工即場可以報警，雖然會唔會告都成問題，同埋最多只罰五皮嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係真嘅，有佢編號人名以後要防禦亦容易好多，例如佢有無喺邊間學校做過，喺邊個 center 返過工，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有無任何違反指引行為</span></strong>等等<br />\n<br />\n<strong>補返少少資料先，「社工」嘅以下變體都唔用得</strong><br />\n(1) 除第(3)及(4)款另有規定外，任何不是名列註冊紀錄冊的人無權使用以下名銜 ─<br />\n(a) 註冊社會工作者」或 「registered social worker」 的稱謂；<br />\n(b) 「R.S.W.」的英文縮寫；或<br />\n(c) 「社會工作」或「social work」 或「社會工作者」或「社工」或 「social worker」 的稱謂，不論是否連同任何其他稱謂或任何英文縮寫使用或以其他方式使用，以描述其專業為社會工作專業或描述其社會工作專業資格。"},{"pid":"dd4b6bf63188ab5f2344944a8a90a5a465b54941","tid":1290650,"uid":26050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"